metadata.name: CryptoDoodez #2
metadata.description: CryptoDoodez! CryptoDoodez are rendition of some of the greatest and most iconic BlueChip NFT projects over the past year. Creation of the founder of KronicKatz, CryptoDoodez serve as a reminder that art is utility as well, thus all who mint have 100% IP rights as stated in the smart contract. Thats right! On chain right for your personal brand now!
